nodes.text: The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught (audiobook)

The New Jedi Order: Dark Tide I: Onslaught is the abridged audiobook version of the novel of the same name, written by Michael A. Stackpole. Read by Anthony Heald, it was published on casette by Random House Audio on June 6, 2000. A digital version of the audiobook was published on February 20, 2007.
